---

---

<section class="proven">
    <div class="container">
        <p class="eyebrow">PROVEN AT SCALE</p>
        <h2 class="heading">50M+ lines of code. Production. Today.</h2>
        <p class="body">
            ChunkHound indexes a 50M+ line monorepo at Applied Materials.
            Sharded USearch HNSW vector indexes with 13 formal invariants.
            Search latency stays flat as your codebase grows.
        </p>

        <div class="card">
            <div class="bar-row">
                <span class="bar-label">1K files</span>
                <div class="bar" style="width: 20%"></div>
                <span class="bar-result">instant</span>
            </div>
            <div class="bar-row">
                <span class="bar-label">50K files</span>
                <div class="bar" style="width: 50%"></div>
                <span class="bar-result">&lt;1s</span>
            </div>
            <div class="bar-row">
                <span class="bar-label">50M+ LOC</span>
                <div class="bar" style="width: 85%"></div>
                <span class="bar-result">still fast</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <blockquote class="testimonial">
            &ldquo;We've compressed what used to take 2–3 months down to 2–3
            days across our 50M+ line monorepo.&rdquo;
            <cite>— Ofir Rozenfeld, Applied Materials</cite>
        </blockquote>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .proven {
        padding: var(--space-10) 0;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .container {
        max-width: 1120px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 var(--space-6);
    }

    .eyebrow {
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-size: var(--text-xs);
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        color: var(--text-tertiary);
        margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    }

    .heading {
        font-size: var(--text-2xl);
        line-height: var(--lh-2xl);
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--text-primary);
        margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    }

    .body {
        font-size: var(--text-base);
        line-height: var(--lh-base);
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
        max-width: 640px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
    }

    .card {
        background: var(--code-bg);
        border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
        padding: var(--space-5) var(--space-6);
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: var(--space-3);
    }

    .bar-row {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0;
    }

    .bar-label {
        font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
        font-size: var(--text-sm);
        color: var(--code-text);
        width: 90px;
        text-align: left;
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .bar {
        height: 28px;
        background: var(--primary);
        border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    }

    .bar-result {
        font-size: var(--text-sm);
        color: var(--code-text);
        margin-left: var(--space-3);
        white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .testimonial {
        margin: var(--space-7) auto 0;
        max-width: 600px;
        padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-5);
        border-left: var(--border-w-accent) solid var(--primary);
        text-align: left;
        font-size: var(--text-base);
        line-height: var(--lh-base);
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        font-style: italic;
    }

    .testimonial cite {
        display: block;
        margin-top: var(--space-2);
        font-style: normal;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: var(--text-sm);
        color: var(--text-primary);
    }
</style>
